    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Manual Door Opener</title>
        <para>The manual passenger entry door opener (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700489">Fig. 89</hotlnk>) is an option that may be required by the state or local
            municipality. The manual door opener assembly control handle (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700490">Fig. 90, Item 4</hotlnk>) is located at the right wing switch panel. The door
            opener transverse rod is situated along the step well and attaches to the door at a mid level height.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700489" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg47/G4700489.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="248px"/>
            <caption>Figure 89. Manual Door Opener Operating Handle</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. BUS KEY IGNITION SWITCH</callout1>
                <callout1>2. DEFROSTER DUCT (ENTRY PANEL REMOVED FOR DETAIL)</callout1>
                <callout1>3. DOOR OPENER SLIDE ROD ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                <callout1>4. FORWARD PASSENGER DOOR PANEL</callout1>
                <callout1>5. DOOR CONTROL ROD</callout1>
                <callout1>6. MANUAL DOOR OPENER ASSEMBLY SUPPORT LEG</callout1>
                <callout1>7. MANUAL DOOR OPENER HANDLE AND CUT OUT</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f4700490" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg47/G4700490.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="240px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
            <caption>Figure 90. Manual Door Opener Transverse Control Rod</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. BUS IGNITION KEY SWITCH</callout1>
                <callout1>2. RIGHT WING PANEL SWITCHES</callout1>
                <callout1>3. PARKING BRAKE SWITCH</callout1>
                <callout1>4. DOOR CONTROL HANDLE AND CUT-OUT</callout1>
                <callout1>5. TRANSMISSION SELECTOR</callout1>
                <callout1>6. RIGHT WING PANEL</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
